snippet.title: Worms 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Worms 2, PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/worms-2/7177/
Playing the first two levels of the sequel of this epic arcade challenge game.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
